{"id": "1337303416837378158", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "254562328769462272", "author_name": "qqinfinity", "author_bot": false, "content": "想請問新人入坑要抽常駐，是要先達成哪一項:\n\n1. 把大多角色抽【到】；沒有要抽滿 多啟/超限\n2. 把一個池的某特定角色抽【滿】；要多啟/超限\n3. 去抽常駐命輪，把巨人之刃或無法完成演算抽【滿】；都疊12", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T06:06:20.470000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337303530855206973", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "254562328769462272", "author_name": "qqinfinity", "author_bot": false, "content": "感覺這三個總要達成不然後續養起來都會亂七八糟 但不知道該從哪個先開始再做之後的", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T06:06:47.654000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337303783692304404", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "254562328769462272", "author_name": "qqinfinity", "author_bot": false, "content": "像我現在就是決定先把巨人之刃抽滿 但珈倫就一直卡在二啟 <:flop:1236937860922343466> (理論上她目標是超限)", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T06:07:47.935000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-02-07T06:08:34.370000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337303896216830023", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "254562328769462272", "author_name": "qqinfinity", "author_bot": false, "content": "但感覺如果真的跑去抽珈倫又會陷入命輪不夠強(輸出無力)的狀況", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T06:08:14.763000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337307261030236221", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "1320994278452887717", "author_name": "galagalaguo", "author_bot": false, "content": "当然是拓展角色池，你觉得输出会无力那就是你牌技差", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T06:21:36.997000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337307308119822418", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 19, "author_id": "870225701855436801", "author_name": "ahuahuahua", "author_bot": false, "content": "我個人比較建議1>3>2\n1.主要是先湊角色打個融災低保\n2.有可能抽到頭破所以我是建議抽命輪", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T06:21:48.224000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1337303416837378158", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337307470611091496", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 19, "author_id": "254562328769462272", "author_name": "qqinfinity", "author_bot": false, "content": "問題是目前我最常看到的問答就是: \n\"我抽到了這個角色 要怎麼用\"\n\"喔 你沒有X啟 / 沒有超限，這隻沒用不需要養\"", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T06:22:26.965000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-02-07T06:48:51.657000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1337307261030236221", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337307574504001557", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "254562328769462272", "author_name": "qqinfinity", "author_bot": false, "content": "然後我腦袋就打結了", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T06:22:51.735000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
