{"id": "1337386572076814447", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "479269844018135040", "author_name": "ekko9950", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@254562328769462272> 首先你要了解\n推幻夢跟主線，只需要一隊，練度只要到超限與+70就足夠了\n打融災需要五個隊伍，也就是19隻角色，融災能給你不錯的養成資源\n相位則是多多益善，除了好玩也可以拿到一些成就獎勵", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T11:36:46.224000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["254562328769462272"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337387592941047912", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "479269844018135040", "author_name": "ekko9950", "author_bot": false, "content": "所以你如果想要不錯過，那些基本的週期資源，就要滿足融災的條件，多抽一些角色，啟靈只是讓角色更強，但角色本身的技能組才是無可取代的東西", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T11:40:49.617000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337387822117683252", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "479269844018135040", "author_name": "ekko9950", "author_bot": false, "content": "我玩到現在，幻夢72000與融災375都達成了，最頂的角色是+75潘，跟一個+12的蠟燭命輪", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T11:41:44.257000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337388165937238028", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "479269844018135040", "author_name": "ekko9950", "author_bot": false, "content": "很多東西不是+36滿配的角色才能達成的，當你的練度能克服許多問題之後，接下來就好好享受遊戲即可", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T11:43:06.230000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
